commit.title: Fix #5351: Intuition does not work with universe polymorphism.
commit.message:
Fix #5351: Intuition does not work with universe polymorphism.

Instead of using non-linear pattern-matching in tauto, we use
constr_eq so as to add the missing universe constraints.
